title: Amy Did Something at Dinner that Embarrassed Her Kids + Is Lunchbox Being Scammed? We Think So… + Bobby Feud: Best TV Shows Of All-Time
itunes:title: Amy Did Something at Dinner that Embarrassed Her Kids + Is Lunchbox Being Scammed? We Think So… + Bobby Feud: Best TV Shows Of All-Time
description:
Amy did something she thought was totally normal while out at dinner recently…but her kids found it very embarrassing. She wants to know if it was weird. We are now convinced that Lunchbox may be getting scammed from his online acting class. We play a heated round of the Bobby Feud where we try to name the most popular TV shows of all-time.
